.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/006-parent-hub-rollout/003-mcp-tooling/spec.md:54:- Define the worked `sk-design/<mode> → mcp-tooling/mcp-figma` design-affecting Figma route as the canonical acceptance and canary scenario [synthesis §7].
