   141	| REQ-007 | Cross-link the two dependent alignment phases so the fallback and eligibility contracts have exactly one home. | `013-create-skill-alignment` and `014-benchmark-alignment` reference this phase's contracts rather than restating them; this spec's RELATED DOCUMENTS lists both. |
