   238	## 12. OPEN QUESTIONS
   239	
   240	- **Q1 (resolved).** The ruling is settled: adopt the phased path (default-on as a staged P4 outcome after P0–P3), decided on the analysis and reversible. An operator override to flip `SPECKIT_COMPILED_ROUTING` on now remains available but is not blocking; the steelman for flipping now is recorded in `decision-record.md` ("flip it when compiled does something legacy can't").
   241	- **Q2.** For the P0 resolver-coupling remediation: promote `resolve.cjs` out of the spec tree into a stable runtime location, or keep it in place behind a path-integrity guard that fails loudly on a renumber? (Recommendation: promote; it removes the drift source rather than guarding it.)
   242	- **Q3.** Which single env profile hosts the P2 canary default-on (repo default staying off), and what parity + clean-fallback thresholds gate promotion from P2 to P3?
