   232	        |
   233	        v
   234	P0 governance + observability
   235	        |
   236	        v
   237	P1 drift CI -----> P2 one-profile canary
   238	        |                 |
   239	        +--------+--------+
   240	                 v
   241	         P3 derived eligibility
   242	                 |
   243	                 v
   244	         P4 staged default-on
